<A NAME="os"></A>
<h2>Operating System and programming language</h2>
<font size='4'>
We use the BrickOS as operating system for the RCX and the programming language C.
</font>

<br><br>

<A NAME="modi"></A>
<h2>Software Modi</h2>
<font size='4'>
We have four software modi in our System:<br>
<ol>
	<li>Seeking for the plant in the room (circle) - when James is seeking for the plant the first time</li>
	<li>Seeking for the window (where the candle's position is close to the room)</li>
	<li>Seeking for the plant on the circle - when James has done his job some times before, the plant stands on the circle</li>
	<li>Observe the window - if the window changes its position, James has to work</li>
</ol>
</font>

<br>

